snippet.title: Gran Turismo® (PSP) Creator Interview
snippet.description:
Prepare for the most authentic handheld racing experience as Gran Turismo debuts on the PSP® system.  Prove your driving skills on 35 tracks and trade or share more than 800 stunning cars from the worlds top manufacturers.

Check out this video to learn what makes Gran Turismo for PSP innovative, as told by Gran Turismo series creator and producer Kazunori Yamauchi himself. Features the song "Lisztomania (Alex Metric Remix)" performed by Phoenix.
